  "content": "<p data-pid=\"_RChUVC6\">强答一波，今天为了答别的题目在翻 Anki 的插件，偶然发现有人已经把我的想法实现了！那就是可以在卡片里链接到其他卡片了！效果如下：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6_720w.gif?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"713\" data-rawheight=\"503\" data-original-token=\"v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"713\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;713&#39; height=&#39;503&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"713\" data-rawheight=\"503\" data-original-token=\"v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"713\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-903670882e117df6e901a3f7fdbe0cc6_720w.gif?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ca5f6ddac2b95df628f72664db1c99d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2121\" data-rawheight=\"1194\" data-original-token=\"v2-8ca5f6ddac2b95df628f72664db1c99d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-95531b1f49dd603072b851aec4bcedcf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2121\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8ca5f6ddac2b95df628f72664db1c99d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2121&#39; height=&#39;1194&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2121\" data-rawheight=\"1194\" data-original-token=\"v2-8ca5f6ddac2b95df628f72664db1c99d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-95531b1f49dd603072b851aec4bcedcf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2121\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8ca5f6ddac2b95df628f72664db1c99d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ca5f6ddac2b95df628f72664db1c99d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"U-ewJujL\">插件页面：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//ankiweb.net/shared/info/1423933177\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">link Cards Notes and Preview them in extra window</a><p data-pid=\"anP9AULz\">有了这个插件，卡片间就可以通过链接联系起来，可以形成 wiki 一样的知识网络。</p><p data-pid=\"cBCLN6z7\">这样一来，当我们复习每个原子知识时，Anki 可以帮助巩固记忆。而平时预览卡片则可以任意转跳，查看有联系的知识。</p><p data-pid=\"ZhwfqyBC\">以上就是我的分享，希望能够对题主有所帮助。</p>",
